title: Wendy Corsi Staub-Shadowkiller
description: Allison Taylor MacKenna finally feels like shes escaped the nightmare that was her life -- but the worst still lies ahead. Detective Rocky Manzillo has discovered that an old photo and a murder victim left without a face share an unexpected connection. And as Allison begins to recall unpleasant details from her past, one who shares her history will try to force her to pay the ultimate price.
